<!-- NEW SECTION 3: LEVEL UP (i+1) - "Visualized Formula" -->
<section id='rumus-ajaib' class='py-24 relative'>
  <div
    class='absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent'
  >
  </div>

  <div class='max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center'>
    <h2 class='text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-2'>Rumus Ajaib</h2>
    <p class='text-(--token-purple-base) font-bold text-lg mb-12'>
      The Comprehensible Input Formula
    </p>

    <!-- The Formula Visualization -->
    <div
      class='flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-16 mb-16 select-none'
      aria-label='Formula: Level kamu sekarang (i) ditambah sedikit tantangan baru (+1) sama dengan pertumbuhan bahasa'
    >
      <!-- Variable i -->
      <div class='group relative'>
        <div
          class='w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 skeuo-card rounded-3xl! flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden'
        >
          <span
            class='text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-gray-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500'
            >i</span
          >
          <div
            class='absolute bottom-4 text-xs font-mono text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest'
          >
            Current Level
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Plus Sign -->
      <div class='text-5xl md:text-6xl text-white/20 font-light'>+</div>

      <!-- Variable 1 -->
      <div class='group relative'>
        <div
          class='w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 skeuo-card rounded-3xl! bg-[oklch(0.18_0.05_293)]! border-purple-500/30! flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden'
        >
          <div
            class='absolute inset-0 bg-(--token-purple-base)/20 blur-xl animate-pulse'
          >
          </div>
          <span
            class='relative text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-(--token-purple-base)'
            >1</span
          >
          <div
            class='absolute bottom-4 text-xs font-mono text-(--token-purple-base) uppercase tracking-widest'
          >
            Challenge
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Equals -->
      <div class='text-5xl md:text-6xl text-white/20 font-light'>=</div>

      <!-- Result -->
      <div class='relative'>
        <div class='text-6xl md:text-8xl animate-bounce'>ðŸª´</div>
        <div
          class='absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-sm font-bold text-white whitespace-nowrap'
        >
          Growth
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Explanation Text -->
    <div
      class='w-full max-w-192 mx-auto prose-lg prose-invert text-(--token-text-secondary)'
    >
      <p>
        Terus, gimana cara nyalain mode Acquisition ini? Nggak perlu otak
        jenius. Cukup pakai satu rumus sederhana: <strong
          >Input yang Bisa Dipahami (i+1)</strong
        >.
      </p>

      <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 my-10 text-left'>
        <div
          class='skeuo-inset p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.05)] border border-white/5'
        >
          <div class='text-4xl font-black text-gray-400 mb-2'>i</div>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-400'>
            <strong>Level kamu sekarang.</strong> Apa yang udah kamu paham. Foundation
            yang udah ada di otakmu.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class='skeuo-inset p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[oklch(0.12_0.03_293)]! border border-purple-500/20 shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.05)]'
        >
          <div class='text-4xl font-black text-(--token-purple-base) mb-2'>
            +1
          </div>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-300'>
            <strong>Sedikit tantangan baru.</strong> Beberapa kata atau pola yang
            belum tau, tapi bisa ditebak dari konteks.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>
        Contohnya: kamu lagi nonton anime. Kamu paham alurnya (i), tapi ada kata
        baru (+1). Karena konteksnya jelas, otakmu otomatis <strong
          >memprediksi</strong
        > celah itu dan "download" pola baru langsung ke bawah sadar. Tanpa sakit
        kepala.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
